commit.message: Merged two git repositories to one git repo

Improve Android app

- Improve graphics and UX
- Clean code base
- Fix geofence bugs
- Disable TTS
- Implement networking with firebase
Added functionality that will post lat and long coords to server
Added internet permission to android app
Added classes for making http requests
this commit contains implementation of text to speech, speech to text and navigation

Implement Android app with locations and geofences

- Add functionality to get current location
- Add functionality to add geofences
- Add functionality to track if devices enters/exits defined geofences
